Name: Average time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Reviewer Agreed after the execution of SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total waiting time to the SW-AE Assign Reviewers following SW-Initial Reviewer Selection
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision across variants that include both activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Time elapsed between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and the subsequent occurrence of Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Cycle time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed eventually occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-AE Assign Reviewers and activity SW-Reviewer Agreed for cases where activity SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Minimum time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Reviewer No Response
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer No Response'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in variants leading to SW-EIC Major Revision
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Average time it takes SW-AE Assign Reviewers after the execution of SW-Reviewer Selection is now due
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer Unavailable in high-latency variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Unavailable'

Name: Average time between consecutive executions of SW-AE Assign Reviewers within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in cases with multiple reviewer assignments
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time for SW-AE Assign Reviewers when followed directly by SW-Reviewer Agreed without reminders
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'
